text: Lamitan, officially known as the City of Lamitan (Chavacano: Ciudad de Lamitan; Yakan: Siyudad Lamitanin; Tausūg: Dāira sin Lamitan; ), is a 6th class component city and de jure capital of the province of Basilan, Philippines. ==References== Category:Cities in the Philippines Category:Provincial capitals of the Philippines Category:Basilan
title: Lamitan
